A(\theta) = \frac{2|v(0)|^4}{3\lambda^2}\sin^3 \theta \cos \theta = C \sin^3 \theta \cos \theta.
\frac{dA}{d\theta} = C \left(3 \sin^2 \theta \cos^2 \theta - \sin^4 \theta\right) = C \sin^2 \theta \left(3 \cos^2 \theta - \sin^2 \theta\right) = 0.
